 id="id-a130c321-6839-453c-bb67-20ad557a9574"><p>periodically reviewing and evaluating the organization’s governance processes;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-d4d5d324-459f-4eb2-8763-5827c9d9f212"><p>adjusting processes according to the outcome of the reviews and communicating changes throughout the organization;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-a0d74e9e-0c53-4791-9b7e-f884ee9d85f6"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="704c5475-4920-4ba2-846d-7bcf59d088c0"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="5191008" change-id="cd503f13-1080-4b9d-f23e-65c1471f051a" text="setting up indicators of gender equality to provide input for the organization’s periodical reviews and the strategic directions;" timestamp="1667422177759"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="5323aa10-e1ec-4068-cdd6-aa341439431c" timestamp="1656590284518"?>establishing prevention, grievance and dispute resolution mechanisms <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="5323aa10-e1ec-4068-cdd6-aa341439431c"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8954503" change-id="1ce0008e-2d84-4072-e8e3-6ee047ff6b98" timestamp="1666866987180"?>in a timely manner<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="1ce0008e-2d84-4072-e8e3-6ee047ff6b98"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="26831e5c-7311-4320-ece1-b0fd71370ccb" timestamp="1667421956193"?> <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="26831e5c-7311-4320-ece1-b0fd71370ccb"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="1bda6b4c-7bfc-4db9-ea13-6a0433bddd1a" timestamp="1656590284518"?>regarding sexual and gender-based violence, including sexual harassment, at an organization level<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="1bda6b4c-7bfc-4db9-ea13-6a0433bddd1a"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="5191008" change-id="8410a541-8eb1-4530-c183-10f50df198f5" text="." timestamp="1667422003219"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="7079f81d-64f2-4da9-a505-81d78f7b0d78" timestamp="1667422003667"?>;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-23db6ee3-191e-4994-ec92-820afa4fbc5c"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7079f81d-64f2-4da9-a505-81d78f7b0d78"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="606ab8a6-1983-4186-ae9e-6d4e7f17b651" timestamp="1674731377367"?>setting clear and specific gender equality targets to all units of the organization and establish a realistic timeframe, accountability and incentives for the achievement of the target</p></list-item><list-item id="id-06ab6795-02c9-41ce-875e-b9df03b307e0"><p>setting up indicators of gender equality according to the actual situation of each organization to provide input for the organization’s periodical reviews and the strategic directions<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="606ab8a6-1983-4186-ae9e-6d4e7f17b651"?></p></list-item><list-item id="id-daa4e2a2-0130-4a17-c1b9-f57b67513e75"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="230259b0-9582-4523-b241-fa18ede53115" timestamp="1667422173093"?>reporting periodically to top management on the status of the organization in terms of gender equality (see <xref as:rid="chunks/id-5910496f-8f7a-4b73-8207-b55ba7c36edf#id-5910496f-8f7a-4b73-8207-b55ba7c36edf" ref-type="sec" id="id-891079da-2faf-4ef0-c930-721abd71008a" xmlns:as="http://niso-sts-authoring-solution/authoring-schema"><?fontoxml-text-placeholder text="type the link text"?></xref> and<xref as:rid="chunks/id-1db31594-c504-4655-a2f5-94a25edc96c7#id-22004143-2e74-44bd-ac75-9277ce4909b6" ref-type="sec" id="id-ad576015-9b3f-4482-f797-64e9ccdcc48b" xmlns:as="http://niso-sts-authoring-solution/authoring-schema"><?fontoxml-text-placeholder text="type the link text"?></xref>) <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="230259b0-9582-4523-b241-fa18ede53115"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="a550fa8a-bf7e-46c7-9358-f024c229faad" text="taking into account structured information that allows to know the achievements of the previous period, to be aware of legal and regulatory modifications and to get the management's inputs and" timestamp="1674569750390"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="0aee4e23-3f95-4997-f156-ee5543b686e3" timestamp="1674569750390"?>including information on past achievements,  demonstrating awareness of legal and regulatory changes, with the aim  of getting management inputs and their<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="0aee4e23-3f95-4997-f156-ee5543b686e3"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="3b535eed-32fb-4cc6-8114-c5741b8ab091" timestamp="1667422173093"?> commitment to new improvement actions.  The content of the management review document can be:</p><list list-type="bullet"><list-item id="id-e8a167e2-23ca-4c97-f9e1-0b449d1795aa"><p>degree of achievement of targets for the previous reporting period<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="3b535eed-32fb-4cc6-8114-c5741b8ab091"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="178d4219-b724-492d-bf4d-2c8f7118e9a8" text="." timestamp="1670338796858"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="7254d6b6-c20f-4946-c79f-5357f950939f" timestamp="1667422173093"?></p></list-item><list-item id="id-c2bec881-9d86-4d05-8c3f-4289fca6e23e"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7254d6b6-c20f-4946-c79f-5357f950939f"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="300c8bc6-8f6c-4094-a176-f12bbb274001" timestamp="1670338782836"?>Gender <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="300c8bc6-8f6c-4094-a176-f12bbb274001"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="c7f63b4d-9b87-40ef-c1c4-22b5c7084011" timestamp="1667422173093"?>equality performance indicators (aligned with those listed in <xref as:rid="chunks/id-f66992e3-bc7e-44ff-8e11-20368eb230a7#id-3e005491-6fc3-44d5-d80c-450eef726792" ref-type="app" id="id-ca799391-0bd0-4a5b-e4d1-668bc4c10e2d" xmlns:as="http://niso-sts-authoring-solution/authoring-schema"><?fon